# Complete test suite for project CRUD operations and browsing

@baseUrl =http://127.0.0.1:5000

### =============================================
### PUBLIC PROJECT BROWSING (No Authentication)
### =============================================

### Get All Approved Projects
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Projects with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects?page=1&per_page=5
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Featured Projects Only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects?featured=true
Content-Type: application/json

### Search Projects by Technology
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects?search=React
Content-Type: application/json

### Filter Projects by Category
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects?category=Web Development
Content-Type: application/json

### Combined Search and Filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects?search=app&category=Mobile Development&featured=false&page=1&per_page=10
Content-Type: application/json

### Get All Projects (Including Pending - for testing)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects?approved=false
Content-Type: application/json

### =============================================
### PROJECT CATEGORIES
### =============================================

### Get All Categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/categories
Content-Type: application/json

